{"tid":2436623,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Tiffany鬆口爆少時有望8月幕前合體","createTime":"2021-03-07T09:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T15:43:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":88,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7fcccd8e03a6becea4c39c304882c6874f0b5f","tid":2436623,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HU3_I6j8p3GZBwfzo11vq_vo5vM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AIVJEJNJ5NEHHALQC3YXAVTF7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHU3_I6j8p3GZBwfzo11vq_vo5vM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAIVJEJNJ5NEHHALQC3YXAVTF7A.jpg&h=165d8b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國女團少女時代（少時）早於2007年出道，經歷前成員Jessica退團後，8位成員感情更加深厚，就算Tiffany、秀英及徐玄於2017年離開舊東家SM事務所，但少時仍未解散，8位成員更不時合體，勾起fans回憶，更有不少fans希望眾成員合體在幕前亮相。<br />\n<br />\n穿打歌服現身<br />\nTiffany亮相昨日播出的JTBC綜藝節目《認識的哥哥》時，鬆口透露少時有望合體演出節目。Tiffany表示：「因為我是8月1日生日，而少時出道日為8月5日，所以通常都是我負責搞派對，一起慶祝生日兼出道紀念日，今年如果能在《認識的哥哥》搞生日派對的話應該很不錯。」就連主持人都紛紛表示贊成，Super Junior成員金希澈更建議少時穿上出道歌《再次重逢的世界》的打歌服登場，Tiffany亦笑言平時都是她決定Dress Code，因而一口接受了希澈的提議，令fans大呼驚喜及期待。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AwMuzDEnYX32AA8DmRJjz1LNvkE=/802x2678/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WBKKHQTGQVDOPK2V5GIF2HFPU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAwMuzDEnYX32AA8DmRJjz1LNvkE%3D%2F802x2678%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWBKKHQTGQVDOPK2V5GIF2HFPU4.jpg&h=396a473d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W3rGtYopIQbIdQBctiANVylrKrE=/802x447/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RXTUMMKVQZAXLKTRQR7NNZPHUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW3rGtYopIQbIdQBctiANVylrKrE%3D%2F802x447%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRXTUMMKVQZAXLKTRQR7NNZPHUM.jpg&h=cb101450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M2IBk7W3dcwicfz1BIkaEW7vgFY=/802x655/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2RSPKGPTQZHLLGF2WGJUH2ASME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM2IBk7W3dcwicfz1BIkaEW7vgFY%3D%2F802x655%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2RSPKGPTQZHLLGF2WGJUH2ASME.jpg&h=db62d482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vxExlVht0i63UC4mc2SRSGORQSU=/802x510/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NXH6X35FFBCTDJQ4IO56HVBMAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvxExlVht0i63UC4mc2SRSGORQSU%3D%2F802x510%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNXH6X35FFBCTDJQ4IO56HVBMAU.jpg&h=71d91884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ao1zn8C-XSRSc857P1HEnMu705E=/802x533/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FOD5ED2V5NCNPHJDK4SFLNEMWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fao1zn8C-XSRSc857P1HEnMu705E%3D%2F802x533%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFOD5ED2V5NCNPHJDK4SFLNEMWY.jpg&h=40a971f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210307/UPKRXDPYLZBGXOKAZG2UDWZQXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210307%2FUPKRXDPYLZBGXOKAZG2UDWZQXA%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeY